title: Andheri Raat Mein Diya Tere Haath Mein
subTitle: Two friends join the underworld to make money and to lead a comfortable life. Later, they realise the ill-effects of crime and want to lead a normal life.

title: Ponga Pandit
subTitle: Two fathers make arrangements and marry their young children. However, years later when the nuptials are almost finalised, the girl rejects the boy.

title: Ek Musafir Ek Hasina
subTitle: A runaway bride meets a charming stranger and falls in love with him while tending to his wounds. However, when the man meets with an accident leading to amnesia, he completely forgets her.

title: Roop Tera Mastana
subTitle: Usha, a princess, is killed by her personal secretary Ajith. Later, Ajith coerces a woman who is an exact replica of the princess to pose as her in order to steal her wealth.

title: Dulhan
subTitle: A girl is left distraught by the sudden death of her husband on their wedding night. However, things take a turn when a man resembling her husband arrives in the village.

title: Maang Bharo Sajana
subTitle: Chandra, a college student, loves Gita and wishes to marry her. When Gita's father discovers this, he rejects his proposal claiming that Chandra is not the biological son of his mother Sita.

title: Suraj
subTitle: King Vikram arranges his daughter Anuradha's match with his commander's son Pratap. However, trouble strikes when Anuradha is abducted by a bandit Suraj when she goes to attend Pratap's coronation.

title: Tyagi
subTitle: Shankar, a good man, takes the blame when one of his brothers is accused of a murder. However, when he returns from jail, he realises that his brothers are trying to create a rift in the family.

title: Dosti
subTitle: A series of unfortunate events causes Ramu, a young boy, to lose his parents and his legs. He is befriended by Mohan, a boy with visual impairment, and they team up to survive on the streets.

title: Dosti
subTitle: A series of unfortunate events causes Ramu, a young boy, to lose his parents and his legs. He is befriended by Mohan, a boy with visual impairment, and they team up to survive on the streets.

title: Clerk
subTitle: Bharat, a poor but honest clerk, sells state secrets under pressure from his family's financial dependence. Realizing his mistake, he chooses to fight and make things right.

title: Shiv Sati Vivah
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Leader
subTitle: Vijay is a rebellious law student who boldly criticises the government, flirts with a beautiful woman and invites trouble. But his life changes when he is accused of assassinating a politician.

title: Bhagwaan Dada
subTitle: Bhagwaan, a reformed criminal, rescues Swaroop, a naive villager. Swaroop rescues Bijli, a young woman targeted by Shambu. The situation regresses when Shambu decides to exact revenge.

title: Kanyadaan
subTitle: Rekha and Amar are married off in their childhood. Years later, Rekha learns about Amar's wedding to Lata and Kumar's real identity.

title: The Emperor of the Mughals
subTitle: A storm brews inside the royal palace and threatens to swallow up the entire kingdom, as a Mughal emperor's pride clashes with the blossoming love between his son and a court dancer.

title: Saudagar
subTitle: Moti betrays his loyal wife and business partner, Majubee, to marry his true love, Phoolbanu. However, his selfish act unleashes unforeseen consequences that upend his life.

title: Balidaan
subTitle: Police Inspector Vijay makes an enemy of bandit Ranga after he kills one of his men. After the vengeful Ranga wilfully abducts Vijay's wife and daughter, he must race against time to save his family.

title: Balidaan
subTitle: Police Inspector Vijay makes an enemy of bandit Ranga after he kills one of his men. After the vengeful Ranga wilfully abducts Vijay's wife and daughter, he must race against time to save his family.

title: Deewaangee
subTitle: Shekhar's pursuit of easy wealth puts his family in peril when they're taken hostage as a fallout from his ill-fated choices.

title: Hum Paanch
subTitle: Thakur Vir Pratap Singh, a landlord, rules over a town with an iron fist and crushes anybody who opposes him. However, unable to put up with his atrocities, five men join hands to destroy him.

title: Agent Vinod
subTitle: Vinod, a flamboyant secret agent, is assigned to investigate the kidnapping of an eminent scientist. Enlisting the help of the scientist's daughter, Anju, he confronts the abductors.

title: Bramachari
subTitle: Brahmachari, who was abandoned as a child, lives in a mortgaged house with 12 young orphans. Things take a turn when he saves a young woman from dying.

title: Amrit
subTitle: A widowed man and woman face abuse from their respective children and seek comfort from each other instead.

title: Sharmeelee
subTitle: A man meets a girl at a rest house and falls in love with her. However, on the day of their marriage, he is shocked to be betrothed to her twin sister.

title: Mera Gaon Mera Desh
subTitle: When Ajit, a former prisoner, learns of Jabbar who is terrorising the people of his village, he decides to stand up against him. However, things take a turn when Jabbar abducts Ajit's lover.

title: Dadagiri
subTitle: Barkha, a young heiress, is abused by her uncle and his family for her inheritance. Later, she runs away but is captured and taken back to her abusive relatives by her mother's ex-lover, Dharma.
